Package: gnome-shell-extension-stage-manager
Architecture: all
Depends: gnome-shell (>= 45), ${misc:Depends}
Description: macOS Stage Manager-like window management for GNOME
 This GNOME Shell extension provides a macOS Stage Manager experience:
 .
  * Maximized windows automatically move to their own workspace
  * A left-side sidebar shows thumbnails of inactive windows
  * Click a thumbnail to switch to that window
  * Auto-hide sidebar with smooth animations
 .
 Compatible with GNOME 45+, works on both Wayland and X11.
